          "value": ""
        },
        {
          "alias": "description",
          "culture": "vi-VN",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "\u00DD ki\u1EBFn ph\u1EA3n h\u1ED3i c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n \u2014 d\u00F9 l\u00E0 b\u00ECnh lu\u1EADn, \u0111\u00E1nh gi\u00E1 hay g\u00F3p \u00FD \u2014 \u0111\u1EC1u v\u00F4 c\u00F9ng qu\u00FD gi\u00E1 \u0111\u1ED1i v\u1EDBi t\u00F4i. \u0110i\u1EC1u n\u00E0y gi\u00FAp c\u1EA3i thi\u1EC7n d\u1EF1 \u00E1n v\u00E0 \u0111\u1ECBnh h\u00ECnh c\u00E1c b\u1EA3n c\u1EADp nh\u1EADt trong t\u01B0\u01A1ng lai. N\u1EBFu b\u1EA1n c\u00F3 b\u1EA5t k\u1EF3 c\u00E2u h\u1ECFi ho\u1EB7c \u00FD t\u01B0\u1EDFng n\u00E0o, xin vui l\u00F2ng li\u00EAn h\u1EC7!"
        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": "vi-VN",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Thank You for Choosing"
        },
        {
          "alias": "content",
          "culture": "vi-VN",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "ce29b0ab-aebc-44dc-bb27-e2b63400ecbb",
      "key": "ed6c08a2-9b86-4524-bdf0-48240315b602",
