            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESPECIAL:\u0026nbsp;\u003C/strong\u003EWe also offer a\u0026nbsp;\u003Cstrong\u003ELOW COST premium\u0026nbsp;\u003C/strong\u003Eversion for those who want exclusive\u0026nbsp;customization tailored to their personal style. Your support means a lot to us!\u003C/p\u003E"
