                    "alias": "classIcon",
                    "culture": "vi-VN",
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "fa-check"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "list",
                    "culture": "vi-VN",
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "C\u00E1c website doanh nghi\u1EC7p v\u00E0 c\u1ED5ng th\u00F4ng tin \u0111i\u1EC7n t\u1EED doanh nghi\u1EC7p\nC\u00E1c trang s\u1EA3n ph\u1EA9m v\u00E0 chi\u1EBFn d\u1ECBch marketing\nC\u00E1c \u0111\u1ED9i ng\u0169 l\u1EADp tr\u00ECnh vi\u00EAn mu\u1ED1n c\u00F3 m\u1ED9t \u0111i\u1EC3m kh\u1EDFi \u0111\u1EA7u chuy\u00EAn nghi\u1EC7p, \u0111\u1ED3ng nh\u1EA5t\nC\u00E1c agency mu\u1ED1n b\u00E0n giao s\u1EA3n ph\u1EA9m nhanh h\u01A1n m\u00E0 kh\u00F4ng ph\u1EA3i \u0111\u00E1nh \u0111\u1ED5i ch\u1EA5t l\u01B0\u1EE3ng"
                  }
                ]
              },
