                        "url": "https://www.orifarm.com/",
                        "queryString": null,
                        "culture": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "description",
                    "culture": "vi-VN",
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Tr\u1EA3i nghi\u1EC7m c\u1EE7a t\u00F4i \u0111\u00E3 v\u01B0\u1EE3t xa m\u1ECDi mong \u0111\u1EE3i! Kh\u00F4ng ch\u1EC9 s\u1EA3n ph\u1EA9m \u0111\u00E1p \u1EE9ng ho\u00E0n h\u1EA3o nhu c\u1EA7u c\u1EE7a t\u00F4i, m\u00E0 s\u1EF1 ph\u1EA3n h\u1ED3i nhanh ch\u00F3ng c\u00F9ng tinh th\u1EA7n s\u1EB5n s\u00E0ng h\u1ED7 tr\u1EE3 c\u1EE7a t\u00E1c gi\u1EA3 th\u1EF1c s\u1EF1 l\u00E0 m\u1ED9t \u0111i\u1EC3m kh\u00E1c bi\u1EC7t l\u1EDBn. Ch\u00FAc t\u00E1c gi\u1EA3 t\u00E0i n\u0103ng n\u00E0y s\u1EBD c\u00F3 th\u00EAm nhi\u1EC1u d\u1EF1 \u00E1n xu\u1EA5t s\u1EAFc h\u01A1n n\u1EEFa trong t\u01B0\u01A1ng lai. Khen ng\u1EE3i cho m\u1ED9t s\u1EA3n ph\u1EA9m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c ho\u00E0n thi\u1EC7n m\u1ED9t c\u00E1ch xu\u1EA5t s\u1EAFc!"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "image",
                    "culture": "vi-VN",
